          sudo ddcutil detect<br>
          sudo ddcutil capabilities<br>
      <br>
      If ddcutil detects the display, its output should tell us the
      monitor model and PNP ID, which is what we need to create or
      update a ddccontrol-db monitor definition.<br>
      <br>
      Best regards,</p>
    <p>Lars Tobias</p>
